==== SOURCE

https://www.ibm.com/industries/healthcare

==== AGENT

IBM		

==== GOAL

The goal is to diagnose the illness and suggest the respective treatments.

==== DATA

The dataset includes the various symptoms from the user and their past medical records.

==== METHODS

IBM Watson is a system based on cognitive computing.
Cognitive computing is a technique which is a mixture of different techniques such as machine learning, natural language processing, reasoning etc.
It analyzes the symptoms, the user's medical history and queries proposed by the user and suggests the treatement accordingly.

==== RESULTS

Watson has been deployed in several hospitals and medical centers in recent years.

==== COMMENTS

It can only process the symptoms as it is stated by the user and it cannot diagnose the internal illness.